name: Scazlab2016
tagline: A repo for the code I write in preparation for and while working at Yale's Social Robotics Lab for 2016
body: In this section I will show the work I did in preparation for the lab, do a daily write up of the code I am writing and the problems I am facing when I am working at the lab and at the end of the summer, feature the paper I have written.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
